    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ZENITH</strong> is a standalone prequel for '<i>They Speak From The Abyss</i>' (Coming 2027)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THEY SPEAK FROM THE ABYSS: ZENITH</strong> is a twisted homage to classic dungeon crawling RPGs. Set in a cursed world filled with the tortured souls in a hellish dimension. Most of which are just trying to live out their eternal suffering in some sort of peace. Explore beautifully gruesome environments, solve sinister puzzles, and confront the woeful souls and frightening demons lurking throughout the <i>Abyss</i>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic dungeon crawlers, the world of <strong>THEY SPEAK</strong> is filled with NPCs, secrets and bits of lore. Wander through the labyrinthine halls and alleys of the City of Dis, battle your way through the Blood Bog, and face your fears in the sinister Mansion Melancholia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/69527a4d953c1bf822ae1f21f0e5a703.poster.avif?t=1761239338\" width=780 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/69527a4d953c1bf822ae1f21f0e5a703.webm?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/69527a4d953c1bf822ae1f21f0e5a703.mp4?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many encounters are pre-set, while random encounters are possible in more threatening parts of the game world. Battles are turn-based, and require deft usage of your weapons, items and skills. Fill out and consult the Grimoire to learn everything you can about your foes, and prepare for your next encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/d9bcd899b5215b201fba73fab164b47f.poster.avif?t=1761239338\" width=780 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/d9bcd899b5215b201fba73fab164b47f.webm?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/d9bcd899b5215b201fba73fab164b47f.mp4?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPEAK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not every demon in <strong>THEY SPEAK</strong> is out for blood. Whether that be in the dungeon or mid-combat, you can always try to Commune with those you encounter. This can provide valuable information, unlock alternate options, or save you from an otherwise deadly encounter. Don't be afraid to speak your mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/c5a4d335a8428578849ad5d6099e6407.poster.avif?t=1761239338\" width=780 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/c5a4d335a8428578849ad5d6099e6407.webm?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393290/extras/c5a4d335a8428578849ad5d6099e6407.mp4?t=1761239338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
